OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Fwill increase form the evening but
OL,7,Fthese will be interspersed with
OL,8,Fblustery showers, these heavy at times
OL,9,Fwith a chance of hail and thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,12,Fshowers at first. The showers clear
OL,13,Ffrom the south as cloud spreads north
OL,14,Fduring the afternoon. Gales and rain
OL,15,Fwill follow over Orkney by the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
